title: Dimensional Gateway 5 (2017) [Full Album]
description:

We're so happy to present the final Neogoa Records release for 2017 - Dimensional Gateway 5, featuring some of the most exciting Goa trance music!

07 - Proxeeus - Nyarlathotep [Short Mix] (146 BPM)
08 - Dragon Twins - Shattered Sense (144 BPM)
09 - Negan - Wäwära (150 BPM)
